title: Energy-efficient building, Media room with a big-screen
posting_body: ['We’re here to chat, give advice, and offer smiles.', 'We look forward to hearing from you.', 'BEAM', '1029 South Jackson Street, Seattle, WA, 98104', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 93', 'OR Text', '93', 'to', 'show contact info', 'for more information.', 'Interested In This Unit?', 'Use this link for more details:', '<URL>', 'LIVE ON THE BRIGHT SIDE', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 431 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Light and lively, BEAM apartments feel like a friendly hello.', 'From studios to two bedrooms, we’ve designed every space for style and speed.', 'Wired for the fastest internet, decked out with stainless appliances, and surrounded by windows to let the sunshine in!', 'BEAM offers the best of Seattle’s International District.', 'Explore a bustling community hub, bright with Vietnamese culture, cuisine, and character.', 'Known for its mash-up of markets, mom-and-pop import shops, and authentic culinary hot spots, BEAM shows off Seattle’s sunniest side.', 'Steps from downtown, minutes from Capitol Hill, with a 98 Walk Score, and a perfect 100 Transit Score, and the Seattle Streetcar right out your door.', 'Welcome to the neighborhood!', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets Welcome!', "Some restrictions and fee's may apply.", 'Contact us!', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5 times the monthly rent', 'Driving Directions:', 'I-5 South:', 'Follow I-5 S to S Dearborn St in Seattle.', 'Take exit 164 from I-5 S', 'Take 7th Ave S and S King St to your destination', 'I-5 North:', 'Follow I-5 N to S Dearborn St in Seattle.', 'Take exit 164A from I-5 N', 'Continue on S Dearborn St to your destination', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Sunday:10:00AM-6:00PM', 'RtZ2XuSgR']
